dct_title_s: Wave Hill visitors guide and map (Text)
dct_description_sm: Selected buildings shown pictorially. Panel title. Oriented with north toward the upper right. Designed to be folded to 18 x 11 cm. Includes descriptive index to points of interest and illustrations. Text and illustrations on verso.
